SetVisibleArea doesn't need to lead to media query change handling when paginated (e.g., when doing a SizeToContent around a print preview window).  (Bug 468645)

diff --git a/layout/base/nsPresContext.h b/layout/base/nsPresContext.h
--- a/layout/base/nsPresContext.h
+++ b/layout/base/nsPresContext.h
